HEADWORD: Homologation
<hw>Ho*mol`o*ga"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>homologation</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Civ. & Scots Law)</fld>
